name: ZELLREAKTOR
description:
You are a macrophage - a cell specialized to find, absorb, and eliminate pathogenic microorganisms. Hyphae around you will start to produce conidia that will damage your organism if left untouched.

Controls: WASD - to move

Co-author: Dimitriew W.

Music: Nuisance: Accouchement, Coruscant, Fluorescence
